Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Comment
    Represents a comment made by a user for an interest's point.
    Controller
    Controller class handles the main logic and user interactions of the system.
    DataGatherer
    Represents a data gatherer, a type of user in the system who can post reviews.
    Evidence
    Represents a common evidence with a single url
    EvidenceProject
    Represents the base class for evidences.
    InterestPoint
    Represents an interest point within a map, identified by its name, coordinates, and a QR code.
    MapUniversity
    MapUniversity class manages the visualization and manipulation of the university map, allowing users to filter and navigate through various points of interest represented on the map, such as projects and their locations, and enabling interaction through point selection, review, and update operations.
    Project
    The Project class represents a project entity in the system.
    ProjectManagementService
    The ProjectManagementService class manages operations related to projects within the system.
    Researcher
    Represents a researcher, extending the DataGatherer class.
    Review
    Represents a review, a specific type of evidence.
    User
    Represents a user, serving as the base class for various user types.
    UserCredentialService
    The UserCredentialService class is responsible for managing user credentials and authentication.
    UserInteraction
    A utility class handling interactions between the system and the user.
    Visitor
    Represents a visitor, a type of user in the system.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CharTypeEvidence
    The CharTypeEvidence enum defines character codes for different types of evidence.
    Pilar
    Enum representing different pillars related to projects.
